== Hydra, the Nix-based continuous build system ==

View the Continuous Integration status of Emacs at http://hydra.nixos.org/jobset/gnu/emacs-trunk, or the [http://lists.gnu.org/mailman/listinfo/emacs-buildstatus emacs-buildstatus] mailing list [http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/emacs-buildstatus/ archive].

You can find other Emacs branches at http://hydra.nixos.org/project/gnu .

See Glenn Morris's description of the Hydra interface at http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/emacs-devel/2013-09/msg00205.html

